Comment: 0,0:02:56.48,0:02:59.78,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,With this many people, we\N have a lot to prepare for dinner,
Comment: 0,0:02:59.78,0:03:03.37,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,so we don't want to overwork ourselves serving breakfast.
Comment: 0,0:03:03.37,0:03:04.20,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:03:04.20,0:03:08.79,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,With that in mind, we'll have\N to make the breakfast a buffet.
Comment: 0,0:03:08.79,0:03:09.71,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,What?
