Comment: 0,0:03:17.42,0:03:18.51,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Just live with it, okay?
Comment: 0,0:03:18.84,0:03:20.30,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,We don't have enough staff in the kitchen.
Comment: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:21.01,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Minko.
Comment: 0,0:03:21.88,0:03:24.80,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Cleaning after the guests check out will also be tough.
Comment: 0,0:03:24.80,0:03:26.85,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,The girls also have school.
Comment: 0,0:03:27.26,0:03:30.35,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,We'll stop assigning rooms, and I'll also help.
Comment: 0,0:03:30.35,0:03:32.27,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You took more reservations?
Comment: 0,0:03:32.94,0:03:34.23,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:03:34.23,0:03:36.69,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Didn't I tell you to stop?
