Comment: 0,0:09:30.17,0:09:32.42,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Maybe a little more to the left.
Comment: 0,0:09:32.42,0:09:33.96,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,What are these?
Comment: 0,0:09:35.38,0:09:38.68,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,I'm making an art gallery of some local artists.
Comment: 0,0:09:38.68,0:09:41.47,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,This will get us guests and profit.
Comment: 0,0:09:41.97,0:09:43.18,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Just you watch.
Comment: 0,0:09:43.18,0:09:45.23,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Kissui Inn is going to change.
Comment: 0,0:09:46.23,0:09:48.10,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Ohana, you also– Huh?
Comment: 0,0:09:49.69,0:09:52.69,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}Kissui Inn is going to change...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:09:52.69,0:10:01.41,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}But I wanted to show Ko the\N Bonbori Festival and the Kissui Inn I love...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:10:04.91,0:10:06.87,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I see... a friend?
Comment: 0,0:10:06.87,0:10:08.87,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Comment: 0,0:10:08.87,0:10:11.67,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,We can't take any more reservations, right?
Comment: 0,0:10:11.67,0:10:13.67,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,If this room will suffice.
Comment: 0,0:10:15.01,0:10:16.26,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,This room?
Comment: 0,0:10:16.26,0:10:18.72,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You want to show him the Kissui Inn, right?
Comment: 0,0:10:18.72,0:10:22.51,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Then he can stay here as a friend.
Comment: 0,0:10:24.22,0:10:25.77,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:10:26.31,0:10:28.94,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Is your health okay? Are you okay?
Comment: 0,0:10:28.94,0:10:29.69,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:10:30.60,0:10:33.73,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Well... I've never seen you so nice.
Comment: 0,0:10:36.69,0:10:39.24,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,He's an important friend, no?
Comment: 0,0:10:40.41,0:10:41.45,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yes.
Comment: 0,0:10:41.95,0:10:43.87,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Thank you very much!
Comment: 0,0:10:44.95,0:10:46.37,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Tsurugi!
Comment: 0,0:10:48.75,0:10:50.29,Default,Teacher,0,0,0,,Hello, Minko?
Comment: 0,0:10:51.42,0:10:53.09,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, Tohru—
Comment: 0,0:10:54.38,0:10:56.30,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,I got a glimpse of the princess sleeping.
Comment: 0,0:10:56.30,0:10:58.17,Default,Boy2,0,0,0,,Who's Tohru?
Comment: 0,0:11:04.81,0:11:06.18,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Um...
Comment: 0,0:11:06.18,0:11:07.81,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Hey, Minchi—
Comment: 0,0:11:10.69,0:11:11.85,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,You know what that is?
Comment: 0,0:11:12.23,0:11:14.02,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,She's sulking.
Comment: 0,0:11:14.90,0:11:17.86,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Because you're siding with the Madam Manager.
Comment: 0,0:11:18.40,0:11:21.57,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Tsurugi likes you, Ohana.
Comment: 0,0:11:25.49,0:11:28.08,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That's hard to believe.
Comment: 0,0:11:29.12,0:11:30.33,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,How's the soup stock?
Comment: 0,0:11:30.33,0:11:31.67,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Checking right now.
Comment: 0,0:11:31.67,0:11:33.33,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Minko, wash the vegetables!
Comment: 0,0:11:33.33,0:11:34.08,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:11:35.71,0:11:37.75,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,When you're done with that, get the duck ready.
Comment: 0,0:11:37.75,0:11:38.80,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Okay!
Comment: 0,0:11:39.51,0:11:43.89,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,{\i1}I can still be a cook wherever I go. Tohru's right about that.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:44.64,0:11:50.06,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,{\i1}But... I want to stay here because Tohru's here...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:50.06,0:11:51.60,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Mr. Ren's here...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:52.27,0:11:55.02,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,{\i1}Everyone's... here!{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:11:55.94,0:11:57.23,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Balut!
Comment: 0,0:11:57.23,0:11:59.53,Default,Two,0,0,0,,There's no way we're serving something that eerie.
Comment: 0,0:12:00.03,0:12:01.40,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,I'm sorry—
Comment: 0,0:12:01.82,0:12:02.36,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,What's wrong?
Comment: 0,0:12:02.36,0:12:03.61,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,You tell me!
Comment: 0,0:12:03.61,0:12:07.33,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,The bowls aren't out, and the guests are complaining.
Comment: 0,0:12:09.12,0:12:12.33,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,It's not like I'm having an easy\N time having to change the soup.
Comment: 0,0:12:12.33,0:12:14.54,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,{\an8}Are you saying it's my fault?!
Comment: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:13.92,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Hey Mr. Ren... {overlap}
Comment: 0,0:12:13.92,0:12:17.13,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Oh, no! What's going on with you two?
Comment: 0,0:12:14.54,0:12:17.71,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,{\an8}Why don't you waitresses get the bowls out or something before you make excuses?
Comment: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.88,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,We don't have time to be arguing!
Comment: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.00,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,{\an8}Say that again? {overlap}
Comment: 0,0:12:19.00,0:12:21.59,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,{\an8}This is the kitchen's problem! Don't blame us!
Comment: 0,0:12:19.88,0:12:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to work together. {overlap}
Comment: 0,0:12:21.76,0:12:22.72,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Your heart's like tofu!
Comment: 0,0:12:22.72,0:12:24.47,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,I'm just sensitive! Okay?
Comment: 0,0:12:24.47,0:12:25.80,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,I'm a pure, innocent, sensitive... {overlap}
Comment: 0,0:12:25.05,0:12:26.47,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Shut up!
Comment: 0,0:12:27.18,0:12:29.56,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Don't you want to protect the inn?
Comment: 0,0:12:29.89,0:12:33.52,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,It's a crucial time for us right now.
Comment: 0,0:12:33.89,0:12:35.94,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Please don't fight here!
Comment: 0,0:12:37.15,0:12:38.57,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Please...
Comment: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:47.78,Default,Two,0,0,0,,Have a great trip.
Comment: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:48.91,Default,Two2,0,0,0,,Thanks.
Comment: 0,0:12:48.91,0:12:50.33,Default,Mom,0,0,0,,Dear, say bye.
Comment: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:51.83,Default,Girl,0,0,0,,Bye-bye!
Comment: 0,0:12:53.12,0:12:55.62,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Something doesn't feel right.
Comment: 0,0:12:57.88,0:13:00.96,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I like the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:13:00.96,0:13:09.51,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,It makes me happy when everyone's\N doing their best to make the guests happy.
Comment: 0,0:13:09.51,0:13:12.60,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,But... it's not the same anymore.
Comment: 0,0:13:12.60,0:13:15.77,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Everyone's too focused on the Madam Manager.
Comment: 0,0:13:16.90,0:13:21.61,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Ohana, you know her real intentions, don't you?
Comment: 0,0:13:23.82,0:13:24.99,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Tell me!
Comment: 0,0:13:24.99,0:13:26.49,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I want to know!
Comment: 0,0:13:26.49,0:13:31.91,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,She's the very person who founded the Kissui Inn I love!
Comment: 0,0:13:32.45,0:13:34.00,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Nakochi...
Comment: 0,0:13:37.25,0:13:40.34,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Stuck with her dream, huh...
Comment: 0,0:13:40.34,0:13:41.55,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Comment: 0,0:13:42.38,0:13:44.84,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,She just doesn't know.
Comment: 0,0:13:45.30,0:13:47.84,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Because she's a runner.
Comment: 0,0:13:47.84,0:13:50.76,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Some people can't have their own dream,
Comment: 0,0:13:50.76,0:13:59.60,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,but they can follow someone\N else's dream and make it their own.
Comment: 0,0:14:14.62,0:14:16.79,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Tomorrow's the real deal.
Comment: 0,0:14:17.12,0:14:18.08,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Yeah...
Comment: 0,0:14:18.08,0:14:20.13,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Did you already come up with a wish?
Comment: 0,0:14:20.13,0:14:21.59,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Oh, not yet.
Comment: 0,0:14:21.59,0:14:25.59,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,And what happened to the Kissui Inn's wishing plaques?
Comment: 0,0:14:25.59,0:14:26.92,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,I gave them to you, right?
Comment: 0,0:14:26.92,0:14:29.43,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Well... they seem to be busy.
Comment: 0,0:14:29.43,0:14:30.97,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,What?
Comment: 0,0:14:30.97,0:14:33.56,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Ohana, they're taking advantage of you.
Comment: 0,0:14:33.56,0:14:36.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,That's not it.
Comment: 0,0:14:36.52,0:14:38.94,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,I will go get them for you!
Comment: 0,0:14:38.94,0:14:41.56,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Hey! Wait up, Yuina!
Comment: 0,0:14:42.86,0:14:45.73,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Good evening!
Comment: 0,0:14:49.49,0:14:50.66,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Tomoe?!
Comment: 0,0:14:54.58,0:14:59.96,Default,Taxi,0,0,0,,During the festivals, we get people from all over.
Comment: 0,0:15:01.71,0:15:03.42,Default,Taxi,0,0,0,,Are you from Tokyo, Miss?
Comment: 0,0:15:03.42,0:15:04.88,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,What makes you think so?
Comment: 0,0:15:04.88,0:15:08.34,Default,Taxi,0,0,0,,Well, you have that city grace.
Comment: 0,0:15:08.34,0:15:10.09,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Do I really?
Comment: 0,0:15:10.09,0:15:11.68,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,That hurts!
Comment: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.05,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Stop, Beanman! That really hurts!
Comment: 0,0:15:14.05,0:15:14.76,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,How is it?
Comment: 0,0:15:14.76,0:15:16.43,Default,Mameji,0,0,0,,It's sprained.
Comment: 0,0:15:16.81,0:15:19.27,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,How will we get by like this?
Comment: 0,0:15:19.27,0:15:21.31,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,We'll ask the union for help.
Comment: 0,0:15:21.31,0:15:22.81,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,Oh, that's not possible.
Comment: 0,0:15:22.81,0:15:27.48,Default,Yuina,0,0,0,,We also asked for help, but no one is\N available because of the upcoming festival.
Comment: 0,0:15:27.48,0:15:29.28,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,You're kidding...
Comment: 0,0:15:29.28,0:15:34.62,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,The Madam Manager said that we have to do\N everything the way we used to for the Bonbori Festival.
Comment: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.33,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,That was part of the promise.
Comment: 0,0:15:36.33,0:15:37.91,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,That's just impossible!
Comment: 0,0:15:37.91,0:15:39.96,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,We'll have to beg her.
Comment: 0,0:15:39.96,0:15:42.71,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,We can get by if we use the new way.
Comment: 0,0:15:42.71,0:15:44.33,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I'll do it!
Comment: 0,0:15:44.79,0:15:46.25,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,No! You need to stay put!
Comment: 0,0:15:46.25,0:15:48.21,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I can't stay put!
Comment: 0,0:15:48.21,0:15:51.68,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I'm not going to lose to the Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:15:51.68,0:15:54.68,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,You're going to lose... to the Madam Manager?
Comment: 0,0:15:55.68,0:15:58.43,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Was work a battle?
Comment: 0,0:15:58.43,0:15:59.39,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,What are you...
Comment: 0,0:15:59.39,0:16:01.02,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,It's just wrong!
Comment: 0,0:16:01.02,0:16:05.23,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Is it more important to win than\N make the guests feel comfortable?
Comment: 0,0:16:05.23,0:16:07.77,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,If we lose, the Kissui Inn will close!
Comment: 0,0:16:07.77,0:16:08.48,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,But—
Comment: 0,0:16:08.48,0:16:10.07,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Do you really understand that?!
Comment: 0,0:16:11.95,0:16:13.61,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Nako...
Comment: 0,0:16:13.61,0:16:16.91,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I love the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:16:16.91,0:16:18.08,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I really do!
Comment: 0,0:16:18.45,0:16:21.08,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,But this isn't the Kissui Inn.
Comment: 0,0:16:21.50,0:16:24.58,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Please bring back the Kissui Inn I love!
Comment: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:26.13,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Please!
Comment: 0,0:16:26.13,0:16:30.80,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,I... finally found a place I could be me.
Comment: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.39,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,"I love the Kissui Inn."
Comment: 0,0:16:37.39,0:16:40.77,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Everyone there felt the same way.
Comment: 0,0:16:40.77,0:16:44.69,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Yet somehow, their feelings slipped past each other.
Comment: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:47.81,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Kissui Inn... 'Tis a castle...
Comment: 0,0:16:47.81,0:16:51.32,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,in a long lost dream.
Comment: 0,0:16:53.90,0:16:54.91,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Excuse me?
Comment: 0,0:16:54.91,0:16:58.03,Default,Jiro,0,0,0,,Oh, I was just speaking your thoughts.
Comment: 0,0:16:59.08,0:17:01.79,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I'll do it in your place.
Comment: 0,0:17:02.41,0:17:03.66,Default,Everyone,0,0,0,,Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:17:03.66,0:17:06.21,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I'll work as a waitress.
Comment: 0,0:17:06.21,0:17:09.25,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I should be able to fill in for Tomoe to an extent.
Comment: 0,0:17:09.67,0:17:11.55,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,B-But...
Comment: 0,0:17:14.09,0:17:15.09,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Hey!
Comment: 0,0:17:15.09,0:17:16.34,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Mom?!
Comment: 0,0:17:17.64,0:17:19.05,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,I came again!
Comment: 0,0:17:19.05,0:17:20.26,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Why?
Comment: 0,0:17:20.26,0:17:21.64,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,I needed a change of scenery.
Comment: 0,0:17:21.64,0:17:23.56,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Staying for two nights. One adult.
Comment: 0,0:17:23.93,0:17:27.48,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Sis, we're full right now, and we don't have time for you.
Comment: 0,0:17:27.48,0:17:30.32,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Don't worry! I'll sleep in Ohana's room.
Comment: 0,0:17:30.32,0:17:33.53,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,If you let me stay, I'll help out too.
Comment: 0,0:17:33.94,0:17:37.32,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,You were yelling in that argument.
Comment: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:40.70,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,And why is no one at the front\N desk when you should be busy?
Comment: 0,0:17:40.70,0:17:42.41,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Mom, are you really going to help out?
Comment: 0,0:17:42.41,0:17:43.83,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,No, you aren't!
Comment: 0,0:17:45.33,0:17:46.08,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Enishi?
Comment: 0,0:17:46.08,0:17:49.13,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,This is our fight.
Comment: 0,0:17:49.13,0:17:53.63,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,If you or the Madam Manager help—
Comment: 0,0:17:55.72,0:17:56.88,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,What?!
Comment: 0,0:17:56.88,0:17:59.01,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Don't run on your emotions!
Comment: 0,0:17:59.01,0:18:02.18,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Don't you want to save the Kissui Inn?
Comment: 0,0:18:02.18,0:18:03.43,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Takky...
Comment: 0,0:18:06.10,0:18:07.85,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Enishing...
Comment: 0,0:18:19.41,0:18:23.70,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,And... it's the day of the festival.
Comment: 0,0:18:30.00,0:18:32.00,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Mom, can I have that?
Comment: 0,0:18:35.88,0:18:37.63,Default,Waitresses,0,0,0,,Thank you for coming.
Comment: 0,0:18:45.10,0:18:47.23,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Yes, immediately.
Comment: 0,0:18:47.89,0:18:50.44,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Takky, the Moon Room needs—
Comment: 0,0:18:50.44,0:18:52.19,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,You're busy?
Comment: 0,0:18:52.73,0:18:53.94,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Ask my sister?
Comment: 0,0:18:53.94,0:18:54.90,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:18:54.90,0:18:57.82,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Young Master, the Moon Room?
Comment: 0,0:18:57.82,0:18:58.53,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,What do they need?
Comment: 0,0:18:59.45,0:19:03.74,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,The yukata's too small. They want size L.
Comment: 0,0:19:03.74,0:19:04.91,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:19:04.91,0:19:07.04,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Thank you very much.
Comment: 0,0:19:07.04,0:19:08.12,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Young Master.
Comment: 0,0:19:09.66,0:19:12.04,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I'm a waitress today.
Comment: 0,0:19:12.04,0:19:14.25,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You need to give the orders.
Comment: 0,0:19:16.00,0:19:16.88,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Madam Manager...
Comment: 0,0:19:16.88,0:19:18.76,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,You have the wrong person.
Comment: 0,0:19:18.76,0:19:20.51,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I'm not the Madam Manager.
Comment: 0,0:19:24.01,0:19:26.81,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm counting on you, Sui.
Comment: 0,0:19:28.02,0:19:29.31,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Minko, how's the vinegar dish?
Comment: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.69,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Just needs the final toppings.
Comment: 0,0:19:30.69,0:19:32.23,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Grill dish is done.
Comment: 0,0:19:32.23,0:19:33.40,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:19:33.40,0:19:35.73,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Can I get the Wave Room next?
Comment: 0,0:19:35.73,0:19:37.11,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,O-Okay.
Comment: 0,0:19:37.57,0:19:39.94,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Nako, I can take care of it.
Comment: 0,0:19:39.94,0:19:40.82,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,But...
Comment: 0,0:19:40.82,0:19:43.07,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,I can still clean with a sprained ankle.
Comment: 0,0:19:43.07,0:19:44.53,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Can you take care of the banquet hall?
Comment: 0,0:19:44.99,0:19:46.28,Default,Nako,0,0,0,,Very well.
Comment: 0,0:19:48.70,0:19:52.33,Default,Two,0,0,0,,Good. Good. Good.
Comment: 0,0:19:52.33,0:19:54.17,Default,Two,0,0,0,,And stop.
Comment: 0,0:19:54.17,0:19:56.38,Default,Two,0,0,0,,You're all good.
Comment: 0,0:19:56.38,0:19:59.51,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I need to check the Crane Room next...
Comment: 0,0:20:01.55,0:20:02.72,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Madam Manager?
Comment: 0,0:20:02.72,0:20:04.09,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Madam Manager!
Comment: 0,0:20:04.59,0:20:06.26,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'm fine.
Comment: 0,0:20:06.26,0:20:08.14,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,I just felt a little dizzy.
Comment: 0,0:20:08.14,0:20:10.43,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Maybe you should rest a little—
Comment: 0,0:20:11.81,0:20:14.81,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,In an inn business, the guests come first.
Comment: 0,0:20:14.81,0:20:17.07,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,We worry about ourselves last.
Comment: 0,0:20:18.53,0:20:22.53,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,But I enjoyed that kind of work.
Comment: 0,0:20:22.53,0:20:23.82,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Madam Manager...
Comment: 0,0:20:23.82,0:20:26.66,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Now, go back to your own job.
Comment: 0,0:20:28.20,0:20:29.24,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.17,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,I'm done over here.
Comment: 0,0:20:36.58,0:20:38.13,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Can you get the stuffing in?
Comment: 0,0:20:38.13,0:20:38.92,Default,Tohru,0,0,0,,Okay.
Comment: 0,0:20:39.38,0:20:40.96,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,Is the Wisteria Room ready?
Comment: 0,0:20:40.96,0:20:41.97,Default,Ren,0,0,0,,Right there.
Comment: 0,0:20:41.97,0:20:42.92,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Keep it up.
Comment: 0,0:20:42.92,0:20:44.80,Default,Minko,0,0,0,,Mr. Ren, the tempura's ready!
Comment: 0,0:20:44.80,0:20:46.39,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I'm taking it to their room.
Comment: 0,0:20:47.64,0:20:49.22,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}It felt so weird.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:49.76,0:20:52.14,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}It's usually just us working here,{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:53.64,0:20:57.48,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}but Mom and the Madam Manager were helping.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:20:55.06,0:20:56.19,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,{\an8}Have a nice trip. {overlap}
Comment: 0,0:20:56.19,0:20:58.57,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,{\an8}Okay, the Happiness Room? {overlap}
Comment: 0,0:20:58.57,0:21:00.94,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,{\i1}I finally realized...{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:02.19,0:21:03.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}my dream.{\i0}
Comment: 0,0:21:33.98,0:21:36.69,Default,Boy,0,0,0,,Granny! Granny!
Comment: 0,0:21:40.15,0:21:42.32,Default,Satsuki,0,0,0,,I'm exhausted!
Comment: 0,0:21:42.32,0:21:44.49,Default,Tomoe,0,0,0,,Everyone's done with dinner.
Comment: 0,0:21:45.90,0:21:47.24,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Good work, everyone.
Comment: 0,0:21:47.70,0:21:50.37,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,Thanks to all of you, we got through.
Comment: 0,0:21:50.37,0:21:52.12,Default,Takako,0,0,0,,For now, let's—
Comment: 0,0:21:52.12,0:21:54.25,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Good, you've rested.
Comment: 0,0:21:54.75,0:21:56.41,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,We don't have time to slack off.
Comment: 0,0:21:56.41,0:21:57.83,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Let's go, everyone.
Comment: 0,0:21:57.83,0:21:58.96,Default,Enishi,0,0,0,,Go where?
Comment: 0,0:21:59.50,0:22:02.21,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,To the Bonbori Festival. Where else?
Comment: 0,0:23:31.76,0:23:34.35,Default,Ohana,0,0,0,,I love you! I love, love, love you!
Comment: 0,0:23:34.35,0:23:37.14,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,If it's possible, I'd like to...
Comment: 1,0:23:38.89,0:23:40.23,Default,Sui,0,0,0,,Dear...
Comment: 100,0:01:51.26,0:01:52.26,Dialogue,Ohana,0,0,0,,{}Ừm...
Comment: 100,0:03:03.33,0:03:04.16,Dialogue,Enishi,0,0,0,,{}Ùh.
Comment: 100,0:03:08.79,0:03:09.67,Dialogue,Nako,0,0,0,,{}Eh?
Comment: 100,0:06:48.01,0:06:48.68,Dialogue,Nako,0,0,0,,{}Eh?
Comment: 100,0:07:01.94,0:07:03.03,Dialogue,Minko,0,0,0,,{}Ừm.
Comment: 100,0:13:40.33,0:13:41.33,Dialogue,Ohana,0,0,0,,{}Ùm.
Comment: 100,0:21:33.89,0:21:36.68,Dialogue,Boy,0,0,0,,{}Ba-ba! Ba-ba!
